This directory contains some (sparse) documentation on the use of NTG.  Here's what here:

  workshop_15sep03.pdf - long tutorial on NTG
  inanc_splines-16sep03.pdf - tutorial on B-splines as used by NTG
  fraga_splines_01aug03.pdf - more details on splines

More documentation coming in the future.

